How to use this script:
* Download it
git clone https://github.com/FloraMaeWolfe/feather-xmr-wallet-getter.git

* Change permissions as needed:
chmod +x feather-xmr-wallet-getter.sh

* Run it:
./feather-xmr-wallet-getter.sh


NOTES:
* This script is currently experimental. It has only been verified to work on Linux Mint 21.2. Other distros have not been tested yet.
* If you enjoy my work and want to support me and my work, there is a file with information on how to do so. 
